OL,3,CQuestions over regulator's handling of
OL,4,Claw firm at centre of #40m fraud probe
OL,6,FRegulators have been ordered to
OL,7,Fexplain how they failed to take action
OL,8,Fbefore the collapse of a law firm
OL,9,Fexposed a suspected #40 million fraud.
OL,11,FPM Law is at the centre of an
OL,12,Finvestigation into what the Solicitors
OL,13,FRegulation Authority (SRA) called a
OL,14,F"sophisticated suspected fraud"
OL,15,Finvolving the misuse of client funds.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
