FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778191868
OL,3,CQuestions over regulator's handling of
OL,4,Claw firm at centre of #40m fraud probe
OL,6,FThe Sheffield-based firm, which was
OL,7,Fmade up of 11 companies, with 25
OL,8,Foffices and more than 30 trading names
OL,9,Facross Yorkshire, Cumbria, Berkshire,
OL,10,FDerbyshire and London, shut down
OL,11,Fsuddenly in February.
OL,13,FIts closure left thousands of clients
OL,14,Fin limbo and hundreds of staff jobless.
OL,16,FNow the Legal Services Board (LSB),
OL,17,Fwhich oversees the SRA, has said it is
OL,18,F"deeply concerned about the failure of
OL,19,FPM Law", especially in light of the
OL,20,Fcollapse of another law firm called
OL,21,FAxiom Ince in October 2023.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778191868
OL,3,CQuestions over regulator's handling of
OL,4,Claw firm at centre of #40m fraud probe
OL,6,FInvestigations into Axiom Ince
OL,7,Fidentified the suspected
OL,8,Fmisappropriation of over #64 million
OL,9,Fin client funds.
OL,11,FThe SRA has commissioned an
OL,12,Findependent review into its handling
OL,13,Fof PM Law.
OL,15,FIt has already said the case is one of
OL,16,Fthe largest and most complex it has
OL,17,Fever faced and it is continuing to
OL,18,Fsupport thousands of former clients
OL,19,Fimpacted by the firm's closure.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778191868
OL,3,CQuestions over regulator's handling of
OL,4,Claw firm at centre of #40m fraud probe
OL,6,FCompensation of almost #10 million has
OL,7,Falready been paid out to affected
OL,8,Fclients.
OL,10,FBut the LSB said it is "concerned
OL,11,Fabout the likelihood of further
OL,12,Fsignificant failures in this class of
OL,13,Fcase".
OL,15,FIt said closer scrutiny and oversight
OL,16,Fof the SRA's handling of "known higher-
OL,17,Frisk firms" was needed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
