PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778191868
OL,3,CQuestions over regulator's handling of
OL,4,Claw firm at centre of #40m fraud probe
OL,6,FIn a statement it said: "This week,
OL,7,Fthe LSB board asked the SRA board to
OL,8,Fprovide assurance, in an in-person
OL,9,Fmeeting before the end of May, that it
OL,10,Fhas the necessary expertise and
OL,11,Foversight approach to deliver the
OL,12,Furgent reform needed to address the
OL,13,Fchallenges and complexities in the
OL,14,Fsector."
OL,16,FMonisha Shah, chair of the LSB, said:
OL,17,F"The LSB's primary concern is
OL,18,Fconsumers: those who have already
OL,19,Fsuffered harm and those who remain at
OL,20,Frisk.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
