PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778191868
OL,3,CQuestions over regulator's handling of
OL,4,Claw firm at centre of #40m fraud probe
OL,6,F"People must be able to use legal
OL,7,Fservices with confidence that
OL,8,Feffective regulation is in place to
OL,9,Fprotect them, particularly from loss
OL,10,Farising from alleged criminal
OL,11,Factivity."
OL,13,FThe SRA has been approached for
OL,14,Fcomment.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
